name: What's wrong with my Shield?
description:
Works inspired by the conditions of my country, Indonesia. This work was released at PISANGSEGER#2 Printmakingzine 2004. 

It's been a long time, but it doesn't feel like it was just yesterday. Together with friends, did an exploration of the art of printmaking in magazine packaging.
The reunion with a friend turned out to have the same hope, this country will improve soon, there will be social justice and prosperity for its people. 
How about releasing the PISANGSEGER Printmakingzine#3 soon..??

Selamat HARI PAHLAWAN, 10 November 2021
